comments.body:
Since C++20, all of these comparison functions can be replaced with just:

```c++
friend std::weak_ordering operator<=>(const CFeeRate& a, const CFeeRate& b) noexcept
{
    return FeeRateCompare(a.nSatoshisPerV, b.nSatoshisPerV);
}
friend bool operator==(const CFeeRate& a, const CFeeRate& b) noexcept
{
    return FeeRateCompare(a.nSatoshisPerV, b.nSatoshisPerV) == std::weak_ordering::equivalent;
}
```

The 4 others will be automatically synthesized from these.

